parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag sensor can cause the airbags to deploy unexpectedly, leading to injuries or accidents, or fail to deploy in the event of a crash, increasing the risk of injury or fatality.

airbags fail to deploy in a crash

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unexpected deployment of airbags can cause injuries, accidents, or distractions while driving, leading to a loss of control or crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in a crash can increase the risk of injury or fatality, as the occupants may not be properly protected.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can cause unexpected deployments, failures to deploy, or false warnings, leading to a loss of confidence in the safety features of the vehicle.

the seat belt buckle gets stuck in the housing
the seat belt is unable to be buckled.

inability to stop the vehicle
